                  </persName> was indicted<rs id="t18431023-2841-offence-1" type="offenceDescription">
                     <interp inst="t18431023-2841-offence-1" type="offenceCategory" value="theft"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18431023-2841-offence-1" type="offenceSubcategory" value="pocketpicking"></interp> for stealing, on the <rs id="t18431023-cd-16" type="crimeDate">
                        <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18431023-2841-offence-1 t18431023-cd-16"></join>26th of Sept</rs>., 1 purse, value 1<hi rend="italic">s</hi>.; 1 half-crown, and 3 shillings; the property of <persName id="t18431023-name-196" type="victimName">
                        <interp inst="t18431023-name-196" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                        <interp inst="t18431023-name-196" type="surname" value="GREEN"></interp>
